				<td colspan="2"><span>    I've been thinking.. E'ci is like a skeleton server on the fact that ppl want to help others, no one is ever open to help.. sooo, I ran to fear and did break in at lvl61 and kited all the adds... pulled my first amy, And then I heard the Zonewide message that Cazic Thule makes when he spawns =-) Ruh roh.... So, I look on track and he's there... so I think.. My track isn't great, so he's close I bet... I wait like 15 min, then run to the temple and pull another amy.. I hear something along the lines of &quot;Denizens of Fear! Come to Aide your Master!&quot; or something like that. I agro'd CT =-P.. so, I hit my gate pot, start running in circles waiting for death.. go DT'd, got corpse summon in Guild Lobby and rez'd.. anyways, now to the point. 
<br />

<br />
     I went back today (lv 63, have FM now) and zoned in, ran to NW corner, and faded. kited off adds that saw invis and followed me far enough to keep agro.... I run to pull an amy, and low and behold, there's my good ole friend CT.. still up.. still deadly.. and still calling friends to DT me.. soooo, dunno how I'm going to do PoFear now w/ CT up.. does he ever go away from the amy temple?</span></td>
